latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Men's Fall-Winter 2024 Show. Evoking the iconography of the American Western wardrobe, cowboy-inspired silhouettes and workwear details are reinterpreted by @pharrell through the Maison's heritage emblems. Watch the full show via link in bio.

#LVMenFW24 #PharrellWilliams #LouisVuitton

Men's Spring-Summer 2024 Show. Presented to a soundtrack produced by Pharrell Williams, the debut show from the Men's Creative Director featured a myriad of vivid hues and captivating motifs, exalting the emblems of the Maison. Watch the full show via link in bio.

#LVMenSS24 #LouisVuitton #PharrellWilliams

California Cool. #LouisVuitton brings together its Art of Living Collections in Palm Springs for the Maison’s latest campaign. See the collection of various trunks, objects, and lifestyle accessories via link in bio.

#LVMenFW23 Fashion Show 
Louis Vuitton presents the Men’s Fall-Winter 2023 Collection, which draws on the formative moments of our upbringing and the rites of passage from childhood to adulthood. See more from the show via link in bio. 

Collection design: Louis Vuitton Studio Homme and Colm Dillane 
Show design, cinematic prelude and show filming : Michel Gondry and Olivier Gondry 
Styling: Ibrahim Kamara 
Creative direction: Lina Kutsovskaya 
Live performance and musical curation: Rosalía

An iridescent effect. Showcasing the signature LV initials with a seashell-like aspect, this season’s Capucines Mini is embellished by an exquisitely braided leather chain. Discover the #LouisVuitton campaign starring Olympia of Greece via link in bio. #LVCapucines

The perfect canvas for reinterpretation. This season, #LouisVuitton’s Capucines takes on tonal colorblock accents as well as a new Flower Chain, which combines gold links and enamel Monogram flowers. Discover the campaign starring Olympia of Greece shot in London via link in bio. #LVCapucines

Presenting Generation “V”. #LouisVuitton’s new campaign brings together friends, talents and familiar faces in a tribute to Virgil Abloh’s lasting legacy of unity and inclusivity. Discover the #LVMenFW22 campaign via link in bio.

Directed by Tyrone Lebon.

Pulsing tempo. Reimagined, redesigned and reengineered to deliver a magical and memorable user experience, the Tambour Horizon Light Up is powered by a custom #LouisVuitton-designed operating system. Learn more about the latest model via link in bio.
#LVConnected #LVWatches

#SuzuHirose, #EbizoIchikawa, #Rola, #Kōki, #Nissy, #RinkoKikuchi and other guests at the #SeeLV opening in Tokyo. Learn about #LouisVuitton’s latest exhibition that celebrates the Maison’s history via link in bio.

Bold tint. Carrying a red edition of the Capucines that perfectly complements her style, Olympia of Greece exemplifies the iconic bag’s femininity and elegance. Discover the #LouisVuitton campaign shot in London via link in bio. #LVCapucines

Olympia of Greece and the Capucines. #LouisVuitton presents this season’s editions of the iconic Capucines bag, embodied by the Friend of the House in London. Discover the new campaign via link in bio. #LVCapucines

Colorful expressions. #LouisVuitton unveils new editions of Taurillon Monogram and Monogram Macassar in a rainbow of hues that refer to Virgil Abloh’s first fashion show for the Maison. Discover the latest pieces in the #LVMen leather goods collection via link in bio.

Louis Vuitton Virtuosity. Unexpected possibilities flourish in Florescence, bedecked with 174.63 carats of indicolite and 164.18 carats of rubellite tourmalines for a blossoming, harmonious contrast — a play of colors and Louis Vuitton's iconic codes, showcased with by House Ambassador Ana de Armas. Explore the creations via link in bio.

At the nexus of technical mastery and emotion, Apogée evokes the heritage savoir-faire of Louis Vuitton virtuosos through meticulous craftsmanship and emblematic details —  revealing a powerful balance of femininity, determination, and artistry. Explore the creations via link in bio.

Louis Vuitton Virtuosity. Showcased by House Ambassador Ana de Armas with a pure radiance, the exquisite necklace of Eternal Sun glows at the apex of brilliance with 27 yellow diamonds, an exclusive 3.88-carat LV Monogram Star cut diamond, and a magnificent 14-carat round yellow diamond — a breathtaking golden spiral expressing genius through minimalism. Discover the new collection via link in bio.
